HEADWORD: opepe
<hw>opepe</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A large African forest tree
(<spn>Nauclea diderrichii</spn>) yielding a strong hard yellow to golden
brown lumber; sometimes placed in genus <gen>Sarcocephalus</gen>, and
then called <spn>Sarcocephalus diderrichii</spn>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> <spn>Nauclea diderrichii</spn>, <spn>Sarcocephalus
diderrichii</spn>.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

